ABOUT US

SK Overseas Consultants & Immigration Services is one of the Leading Immigration Services Company in India, Specialized in all kind of Visa's and providing solutions to our clients who intend to relocate to other countries.

With years of experience, we have an exceptional list of successful clients. SK Overseas Consultants is well poised to deliver authentic and quality immigration services. SK Overseas Consultants is run based on certain principles like honesty, transparency, integrity and as a result of this we have over 98.5% of success rate.

SK Overseas Consultants is the top immigration consultants specialist for Australia and Canada. The company manages the administrative and non-judgmental tasks related to visa, passport, identity management and other citizen services for its clients. This enables them to focus entirely on the critical task of assessment.

The company has successfully processed over 6 thousand applications since its inception in 2018..

SK Overseas Consultants provides a wide range of services to visa applicants, all aimed at enhancing customer experience in services with an automated and seamless process. However SK Overseas Consultants does not play any part in the decision-making process behind visa applications being granted or denied.

SK Overseas Consultants employs highly trained and dedicated staff, and is continually investing in its people and technology operations. The company offers rewarding and exciting career opportunities across the globe.
